    {
      "id": "1944750c-f3ba-8042-b4cf-e63fdb995c54",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Implementing different learning analytics systems is often described in isolation, but often, the combined systems that can be integrated are not discussed holistically. The authors describe their Experience API in Learning Tools Interoperability. The authors discuss challenges regarding multiple aspects, such as organization, methodology, content didactics and technology.",
